Drozdovska Marta Chapter-8 ex 27
This algorithm is a tringular matrix ,where we record the position of the words
and it looks like:
    |a11  a12  a13|
    |0    a22  a23|
    |0    0    a33|
    The horisontal axis will denote the end position , the vertical axis will denote the start  position
    
